            <div class="title">
                Finance Bill Amendments (Chairman&#39;s Selection)
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1951-06-21/debates/7b9b13a0-2f98-44d4-a0c2-8f6ac4a49ed4/Persia(Anglo-IranianOilCompany)" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
